{
  "texts": [
    "Primary features.",
    "In order to ensure meaningful security evaluation of targeted SIEM solutions, it is important that all the essential features are considered.",
    "Thus we perform a detailed evaluation of these features for each SIEM solution and determine if the feature is missing, or has either a basic-level or advanced-level implementation.",
    "One of the most important features for evaluating a SIEM system is its capability to detect events at high speed.",
    "The speed is measured in terms of EPS."
  ]
}